  </section>

  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-4xl prose prose-lg mx-auto">
        <h2>Midway Airport Black Car Service</h2>
        <p>Midway International Airport (MDW) serves millions of passengers annually. Our professional black car service provides reliable transportation to and from Midway with the same high standards you'd expect from a premium car service.</p>
        <p>Unlike O'Hare's sprawling terminals, Midway offers a more compact layoutâ€”but that doesn't mean ground transportation is any less important. Our chauffeurs know the best pickup locations, navigate Cicero Avenue traffic efficiently, and provide the professional service that makes every trip stress-free.</p>
        
        <h3>Why Choose Our Midway Airport Service?</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Real-time flight tracking for all Midway arrivals</li>
          <li>Curbside pickup or meet-and-greet options</li>
          <li>Fixed pricing with no surge rates</li>
          <li>Professional, licensed chauffeurs</li>
          <li>Premium fleet with sedans, SUVs, and vans</li>
          <li>24/7 availability including holidays</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Midway to Downtown Chicago</h3>
        <p>The route from Midway to downtown Chicago typically takes 25-35 minutes depending on traffic. Our chauffeurs use real-time traffic data to select the most efficient route, whether that's via I-55 or alternative routes during rush hour.</p>

        <h3>Midway to Chicago Suburbs</h3>
        <p>We provide service from Midway to all Chicago suburbs, including southwestern communities like Oak Lawn, Burr Ridge, and Orland Park, as well as northern and western suburbs throughout the metropolitan area.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-12 bg-gray-900 text-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Book Your Midway Airport Transfer</h2>
